  "body": "This fixes a regression (crash) introduced in 0.62.0. For the full list of changes in 0.62, see [here](https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/releases/tag/v0.62.0).\r\n\r\n<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at v0.62.1 -->\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n### Fixes 🔧\r\n* Fix crash when keybindings are disabled that normally show in the status bar by @stefanhaller in https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/pull/5655\r\n### Docs 📖\r\n* Add docs for how to add the default, non-pager diff to the list of pagers by @stefanhaller in https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/pull/5656\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/compare/v0.62.0...v0.62.1\r\n\r\n",
